      "content": "the problem is i tried to tell my friends but they think i'm just being paranoid or unhinged. they said i'm just \"posting differently\" lately. but it's not just different... it's like i'm seeing a completely different person inhabit my life. i even saw a post today where it talked about a childhood memory i *never* shared publicly. how would it even know that? isn't there a way to track if someone is actually using my data to train a version of me?",
